ugp.org.javafx.beans

Interface IPropertyContainer<T extends javafx.beans.property.Property<?>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneralTransition, PropertiesList

    public interface IPropertyContainer<T extends javafx.beans.property.Property<?>>
    Abstract property container. Supposed to be implemented by object that contains properties (bean object) or by object that is further developing this ones functionality, such as PropertiesList.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    PETO
